{"title":"In Stock for Now: The Radavist Summer 2024 Merch","link":"https://theradavist.com/the-radavist-summer-2024-merch/","date":1718378187000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"5999\" height=\"3999\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Drop.jpg?fit=1200,3999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Drop.jpg?w=5999&amp;quality=75 5999w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Drop.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Drop.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Drop.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Drop.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Drop.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>We’ve got some fresh threads for your feet and head in our Summer 2024 merch drop!</p>\n<p>We’ve finally found our summer sock supplier with a small US manufacturer that has developed the comfiest socks yet. Seriously, these socks are the best-feeling summer-weight wool socks we’ve ever worn, and we’re not just saying that! We worked hard dialing in the fit and feel after lots of feedback from our customers.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-2.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-2.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-8.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-8.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-8.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-8.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-8.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-20.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-20.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-20.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-20.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-20.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-24.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-24.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-24.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-24.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024Socks-24.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>This drop includes our 1960s pop art pool water-themed <a href=\"https://shop.theradavist.com/products/socks-hockney\" target=\"_blank\">Hockney design in turquoise</a>, two colorways of the <a href=\"https://shop.theradavist.com/products/socks-3-stripe\" target=\"_blank\">3-stripe Klunker sock</a> (a summer staple!), and our <a href=\"https://shop.theradavist.com/products/socks-sidewinder\" target=\"_blank\">Sidewinder socks</a>, inspired by the Mojave Desert Sidewinder’s ability to bury its body in sand, leaving everything but its eyes exposed.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024CampHats-7.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024CampHats-7.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024CampHats-7.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024CampHats-7.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Summer2024CampHats-7.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Adding to the fun are three fresh colors in our Camp Hat design. We went back to our pre-COVID supplier, restyled the hat with a little bit more room in the head, and are offering them in three colors: <a href=\"https://shop.theradavist.com/products/camp-hat-jackal\" target=\"_blank\">Sage, Mallow, and Slate</a>. These new hats feature a plastic buckle, and The Radavist script on the back. Sewn in Los Angeles from made in the USA cotton.</p>\n<p>The Radavist Summer 2024 Drop is in stock today at <a href=\"https://shop.theradavist.com/\" target=\"_blank\">The Radavist Webshop</a>.</p>\n<p><em>As with all of our merch sales, your support pays our team so we can keep the site fresh daily. Every single penny helps, and we greatly appreciate your support! From everyone over here, THANK YOU!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-radavist-summer-2024-merch/\">In Stock for Now: The Radavist Summer 2024 Merch</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba